在1-5题中, 求f(x)在 x = a的线性化L(x)

1. f(x) = x**3 - 2*x + 3, a = 2
    L(x) = f(a) + f'(a)*(x - a) = 8 - 4 + 3 + (3*a**2 - 2)*(x - 2) = 7 + 10*(x -2) = 10*x - 13

3. f(x) = x + 1/x, a = 1
    L(x) = f(a) + f'(a)*(x - a) = a + 1/a + (1 - 1/a**2)*(x - 1) = 2

5. f(x) = tan(x), a = pi
    L(x) = f(a) + f'(a)*(x - a) = tan(a) + sec(a)**2*(x - a) = x - pi

